00:15:53.420 --> 00:15:55.890 align:middle line:84%
>>DOOLEY: The book, like
the Notes From the Universe,

00:15:55.890 --> 00:15:59.930 align:middle line:84%
give me a platform to share
what has stirred in me for

00:15:59.930 --> 00:16:01.160 align:middle line:90%
