you're not ready.

00:28:21.220 --> 00:28:26.130 align:middle line:84%
Number four is, because of what
I teach day in and day out,

00:28:26.130 --> 00:28:29.060 align:middle line:90%
dreams can come true.

00:28:29.060 --> 00:28:31.760 align:middle line:84%
Of course, the chapters
go into great detail

00:28:31.760 --> 00:28:33.470 align:middle line:90%
in each of these topics.

00:28:33.470 --> 00:28:37.540 align:middle line:84%
The idea of dead people having
something to share really

00:28:37.540 --> 00:28:43.260 align:middle line:84%
is kind of obvious if you
believe there's an afterlife.

00:28:43.260 --> 00:28:45.710 align:middle line:84%
And poll after poll,
throughout the United States

00:28:45.710 --> 00:28:47.960 align:middle line:84%
and the world, has
indicated that most people

00:28:47.960 --> 00:28:49.620 align:middle line:90%
do believe in an afterlife.

00:28:49.620 --> 00:28:51.620 align:middle line:84%
Unfortunately, they just
kind of stopped there,

00:28:51.620 --> 00:28:53.950 align:middle line:84%
and they don't know
what to expect.

00:28:53.950 --> 00:28:57.400 align:middle line:84%
I think we can know a
lot about what to expect.

00:28:57.400 --> 00:28:59.710 align:middle line:84%
The point being, if you
believe in an afterlife,

00:28:59.710 --> 00:29:03.990 align:middle line:84%
you believe that we survive the
demise of our physical bodies.

00:29:03.990 --> 00:29:05.820 align:middle line:84%
You know, what's
going to be going on?

00:29:05.820 --> 00:29:10.540 align:middle line:84%
Well, can you imagine
discovering not only

00:29:10.540 --> 00:29:13.900 align:middle line:84%
that you survived, but
you're alive and well,

00:29:13.900 --> 00:29:16.390 align:middle line:84%
and that love is
everywhere, and that there's

00:29:16.390 --> 00:29:19.730 align:middle line:84%
this benign, benevolent
intelligence that's

00:29:19.730 --> 00:29:23.690 align:middle line:84%
kind of wrapped itself around
you, that bathes you in love,

00:29:23.690 --> 00:29:25.770 align:middle line:90%
and approval, and acceptance.

00:29:25.770 --> 00:29:28.220 align:middle line:84%
And then you see those
who've gone before you,

00:29:28.220 --> 00:29:31.350 align:middle line:84%
and you realize they never
died, and that they're intact.

00:29:31.350 --> 00:29:33.900 align:middle line:84%
In fact, they've taken on
the form and the essence that

00:29:33.900 --> 00:29:35.310 align:middle line:90%
pleases them most.

00:29:35.310 --> 00:29:36.490 align:middle line:90%
Their health is restored.

00:29:36.490 --> 00:29:38.020 align:middle line:90%
Their vitality is restored.

00:29:38.020 --> 00:29:39.720 align:middle line:90%
Their good looks are restored.

00:29:39.720 --> 00:29:40.890 align:middle line:90%
They're on new adventures.

00:29:40.890 --> 00:29:42.030 align:middle line:90%
They're on new discoveries.

00:29:42.030 --> 00:29:43.580 align:middle line:90%
They have new places to go.

00:29:43.580 --> 00:29:45.870 align:middle line:84%
They're excitedly telling
you all about this.

00:29:45.870 --> 00:29:50.140 align:middle line:84%
Your mind is just blown
to pieces in a joyful way.

00:29:50.140 --> 00:29:52.420 align:middle line:84%
The possibilities, the
infinite possibilities,

00:29:52.420 --> 00:29:53.830 align:middle line:90%
are all coming together.

00:29:53.830 --> 00:29:55.834 align:middle line:84%
You're starting
to remember things

00:29:55.834 --> 00:29:57.500 align:middle line:84%
that you had forgotten
during your life,

00:29:57.500 --> 00:30:00.520 align:middle line:84%
because we chose to forget
stuff during our lives,

00:30:00.520 --> 00:30:03.020 align:middle line:84%
so that we could kind
of have a reset button.

00:30:03.020 --> 00:30:04.580 align:middle line:90%
That's the amnesia.

00:30:04.580 --> 00:30:06.560 align:middle line:84%
And all of a sudden,
you've got memories

00:30:06.560 --> 00:30:09.800 align:middle line:84%
from other lifetimes, and other
loves, and other passions,

00:30:09.800 --> 00:30:13.390 align:middle line:84%
and other interests,
and this kaleidoscope

00:30:13.390 --> 00:30:17.060 align:middle line:84%
is being fulfilled, and the
dots are being connected,

00:30:17.060 --> 00:30:20.470 align:middle line:84%
and you're just like,
woohoo, oh my gosh.

00:30:20.470 --> 00:30:22.950 align:middle line:90%
It's just all so loving.

00:30:22.950 --> 00:30:25.790 align:middle line:84%
And then, you take a look
back over your shoulder,

00:30:25.790 --> 00:30:29.280 align:middle line:84%
and there's this devastation
in your wake on planet Earth.

00:30:29.280 --> 00:30:32.650 align:middle line:84%
There's these broken
hearts, and there's

00:30:32.650 --> 00:30:35.050 align:middle line:84%
this big hole where
your life once was,

00:30:35.050 --> 00:30:36.710 align:middle line:90%
and all the survivors.

00:30:36.710 --> 00:30:39.290 align:middle line:84%
They're just
distraught, and they're

00:30:39.290 --> 00:30:43.300 align:middle line:90%
in this horrific state of grief.

00:30:43.300 --> 00:30:45.800 align:middle line:90%
What do you think comes next?

00:30:45.800 --> 00:30:49.620 align:middle line:84%
You, more than anything,
want to reach out.

00:30:49.620 --> 00:30:50.710 align:middle line:90%
You want to talk to them.

00:30:50.710 --> 00:30:53.265 align:middle line:84%
You want to shout from the
mountain tops, I'm alive.

00:30:53.265 --> 00:30:54.720 align:middle line:90%
I'm alive.

00:30:54.720 --> 00:30:55.800 align:middle line:90%
It's awesome.

00:30:55.800 --> 00:30:56.780 align:middle line:90%
It's beautiful.

00:30:56.780 --> 00:30:58.160 align:middle line:90%
I see clearly now.

00:30:58.160 --> 00:30:59.850 align:middle line:90%
And you're going to see it too.

00:30:59.850 --> 00:31:01.520 align:middle line:90%
It's all going to make sense.

00:31:01.520 --> 00:31:03.760 align:middle line:84%
But your time and
space isn't done.

00:31:03.760 --> 00:31:06.070 align:middle line:84%
And you can see from
this elevated prospective

00:31:06.070 --> 00:31:07.390 align:middle line:90%
what their challenges are.

00:31:07.390 --> 00:31:09.650 align:middle line:84%
What their
trajectories of growth,

00:31:09.650 --> 00:31:13.300 align:middle line:84%
and discovery, and
joy still will be.

00:31:13.300 --> 00:31:16.590 align:middle line:84%
And so, you want to tell
them that it's awesome,

00:31:16.590 --> 00:31:20.590 align:middle line:84%
but you also don't want
to hasten their desire

00:31:20.590 --> 00:31:22.520 align:middle line:90%
to join you, because game on.

00:31:22.520 --> 00:31:27.040 align:middle line:84%
They're still going through
this fertile season of growth.

00:31:27.040 --> 00:31:29.590 align:middle line:84%
So you're very measured
in what you can share,

00:31:29.590 --> 00:31:31.730 align:middle line:84%
and what you share,
and so you tell

00:31:31.730 --> 00:31:33.330 align:middle line:84%
them both sides of
the coin, that it's

00:31:33.330 --> 00:31:35.320 align:middle line:90%
all so glorious and grand.

00:31:35.320 --> 00:31:37.750 align:middle line:84%
But believe me, on this
side of the equation,

00:31:37.750 --> 00:31:39.490 align:middle line:84%
on the other side
of time and space,

00:31:39.490 --> 00:31:41.670 align:middle line:84%
there's a line of folks
waiting to get back

00:31:41.670 --> 00:31:43.720 align:middle line:84%
into the jungles
of time and space.

00:31:43.720 --> 00:31:45.930 align:middle line:84%
Because from here, we
see how awesome it is.

00:31:45.930 --> 00:31:47.470 align:middle line:90%
We see how perfect it is.

00:31:47.470 --> 00:31:50.710 align:middle line:84%
We see that everyone's becoming
more, and falling in love,

00:31:50.710 --> 00:31:54.502 align:middle line:84%
and creating this
world of their dreams,

00:31:54.502 --> 00:31:56.210 align:middle line:84%
even though they don't
know their creator

00:31:56.210 --> 00:31:58.330 align:middle line:84%
So you want to tell
them, you're creating

00:31:58.330 --> 00:32:00.860 align:middle line:84%
right now as you go
on the fly, that you

00:32:00.860 --> 00:32:02.620 align:middle line:84%
have this divine
sense about you,

00:32:02.620 --> 00:32:06.570 align:middle line:84%
this divine power, that's
innate in all consciousness,

00:32:06.570 --> 00:32:08.900 align:middle line:84%
particularly of
the human variety.

00:32:08.900 --> 00:32:10.610 align:middle line:90%
And so, hang in there.

00:32:10.610 --> 00:32:11.390 align:middle line:90%
Tough it out.

00:32:11.390 --> 00:32:12.890 align:middle line:90%
We're going to be together soon.

00:32:12.890 --> 00:32:18.600 align:middle line:84%
And so, there's these 10 things
that the dead want to tell you.

00:32:18.600 --> 00:32:21.630 align:middle line:84%
Because from their perspective,
they now have all the answers.

00:32:21.630 --> 00:32:23.880 align:middle line:90%
Not all the answers.

00:32:23.880 --> 00:32:25.720 align:middle line:84%
There's still going
to be questions.

00:32:25.720 --> 00:32:29.990 align:middle line:84%
But enough answers to
give all of us blazing,

00:32:29.990 --> 00:32:33.950 align:middle line:84%
brilliant clarity, to kind of
get our groove on, and have

00:32:33.950 --> 00:32:38.190 align:middle line:84%
a roaring time in space while
the getting's still good.

00:32:38.190 --> 00:32:41.180 align:middle line:84%
This is the nucleus,
or the purpose,

00:32:41.180 --> 00:32:45.840 align:middle line:84%
that evolved as I began
elaborating on what was once

00:32:45.840 --> 00:32:50.630 align:middle line:84%
a Note From the Universe, just
a page long, that's now 200-page

00:32:50.630 --> 00:32:51.130 align:middle line:90%
book.

00:32:51.130 --> 00:32:51.580 align:middle line:90%
[END PLAYBACK]

00:32:51.580 --> 00:32:53.538 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I didn't prepare
you for this question,

00:32:53.538 --> 00:32:58.050 align:middle line:84%
but if you were Robin Williams,
and you were to write a note

00:32:58.050 --> 00:33:05.710 align:middle line:84%
back to us, who really, really
miss that man and thought

00:33:05.710 --> 00:33:09.490 align:middle line:84%
so much talent, and he
could've-- we all have our own

00:33:09.490 --> 00:33:10.380 align:middle line:90%
perspectives.

00:33:10.380 --> 00:33:14.550 align:middle line:84%
He could have gotten help,
but we miss him, his talent

00:33:14.550 --> 00:33:16.180 align:middle line:90%
and his person.

00:33:16.180 --> 00:33:18.030 align:middle line:90%
What would he said?

00:33:18.030 --> 00:33:21.440 align:middle line:84%
>>DOOLEY: There's virtually
no doubt in my mind

00:33:21.440 --> 00:33:24.320 align:middle line:84%
that he would echo all of
the things in the book.

00:33:24.320 --> 00:33:26.750 align:middle line:84%
And if you would see he could
have made other choices--

00:33:26.750 --> 00:33:29.470 align:middle line:84%
and I'm not passing judgment
in any way, shape, or form.

00:33:29.470 --> 00:33:34.350 align:middle line:84%
I can't imagine what he went
through, the torment, the hell,

00:33:34.350 --> 00:33:37.020 align:middle line:90%
the man-made hell, so to speak.

00:33:37.020 --> 00:33:42.000 align:middle line:84%
But he would want
everyone to know he's OK.

00:33:42.000 --> 00:33:47.780 align:middle line:84%
He would want everyone to know
that it was not a good choice,

00:33:47.780 --> 00:33:49.440 align:middle line:90%
because others emulate him.

00:33:49.440 --> 00:33:50.410 align:middle line:90%
Others model him.

00:33:50.410 --> 00:33:52.810 align:middle line:84%
Others are going through
their own misery right now.

00:33:52.810 --> 00:33:56.680 align:middle line:84%
And if Robin Williams
can do it, it's

00:33:56.680 --> 00:33:59.350 align:middle line:90%
maybe a respectable choice.

00:33:59.350 --> 00:34:02.920 align:middle line:84%
And he wouldn't want anyone
to follow in his footsteps.

00:34:02.920 --> 00:34:06.370 align:middle line:84%
He would remind all of
us that the greatness

00:34:06.370 --> 00:34:11.050 align:middle line:84%
that we admire in him is alive
in each and every one of us.

00:34:11.050 --> 00:34:13.989 align:middle line:84%
That he is no more
divine or gifted

00:34:13.989 --> 00:34:15.969 align:middle line:90%
than any single human being.

00:34:15.969 --> 00:34:20.190 align:middle line:84%
And that if we so choose,
the best of our lives

00:34:20.190 --> 00:34:21.940 align:middle line:90%
remains in front of all of us.

00:34:21.940 --> 00:34:24.520 align:middle line:90%
And so, weather the storm.

00:34:24.520 --> 00:34:25.580 align:middle line:90%
Hang in there.

00:34:25.580 --> 00:34:27.909 align:middle line:84%
You're going to die
anyway, you might say.

00:34:27.909 --> 00:34:31.929 align:middle line:84%
And create a chuckle or smile,
because life is fleeting.

00:34:31.929 --> 00:34:35.110 align:middle line:84%
And I say that to those--
I hear from a lot of people

00:34:35.110 --> 00:34:35.909 align:middle line:90%
who are suicidal.

00:34:35.909 --> 00:34:38.199 align:middle line:84%
It's like, you're
going to die anyway.

00:34:38.199 --> 00:34:40.380 align:middle line:84%
And in your mind at least,
it's forever and ever.

00:34:40.380 --> 00:34:44.280 align:middle line:84%
And so if you have another 10,
or 20, or 80 years on Earth,

00:34:44.280 --> 00:34:46.620 align:middle line:84%
it's nothing compared
to where you're going.

00:34:46.620 --> 00:34:48.290 align:middle line:90%
What's the hurry?

00:34:48.290 --> 00:34:50.540 align:middle line:84%
For the fact that you're
here, it's meaningful.

00:34:50.540 --> 00:34:52.219 align:middle line:90%
It's profoundly meaningful.

00:34:52.219 --> 00:34:54.480 align:middle line:90%
Life is not random chance.

00:34:54.480 --> 00:34:57.050 align:middle line:84%
We are not space dust
that collided and evolved

00:34:57.050 --> 00:34:57.980 align:middle line:90%
into walking upright.

00:34:57.980 --> 00:35:02.530 align:middle line:84%
That is patently, ridiculously,
offensively absurd.

00:35:02.530 --> 00:35:04.830 align:middle line:84%
And anyone can drill
down to the truths

00:35:04.830 --> 00:35:06.620 align:middle line:84%
that I've drilled
down to in this book,

00:35:06.620 --> 00:35:08.092 align:middle line:90%
because they're so benign.

00:35:08.092 --> 00:35:09.800 align:middle line:84%
I'm not trying to
create a religion here.

00:35:09.800 --> 00:35:11.270 align:middle line:90%
I'm saying life is beautiful.

00:35:11.270 --> 00:35:12.600 align:middle line:90%
We are powerful.

00:35:12.600 --> 00:35:14.290 align:middle line:90%
Eternal sparks of God.

00:35:14.290 --> 00:35:15.190 align:middle line:90%
Let's make hay.

00:35:15.190 --> 00:35:17.820 align:middle line:84%
That's the truths that
I'm claiming in the book,

00:35:17.820 --> 00:35:20.960 align:middle line:84%
and I'm not the first to
have made these declarations.

00:35:20.960 --> 00:35:24.090 align:middle line:84%
And so he is now our
greatest cheerleader.

00:35:24.090 --> 00:35:26.590 align:middle line:84%
And he is helping
where one could

00:35:26.590 --> 00:35:29.850 align:middle line:84%
help in any way he can
help to those on earth

00:35:29.850 --> 00:35:33.430 align:middle line:84%
while calculating
his next adventures,

00:35:33.430 --> 00:35:35.930 align:middle line:90%
and his next challenges.

00:35:35.930 --> 00:35:37.950 align:middle line:84%
Because challenges
are how we grow.

00:35:37.950 --> 00:35:38.700 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:35:38.700 --> 00:35:41.390 align:middle line:84%
So have you had people
read the book who

00:35:41.390 --> 00:35:44.560 align:middle line:84%
have contemplated suicide,
and turned their lives

00:35:44.560 --> 00:35:46.649 align:middle line:90%
around form--

00:35:46.649 --> 00:35:47.940 align:middle line:90%
>>DOOLEY: I'd like to think so.

00:35:47.940 --> 00:35:49.981 align:middle line:84%
It's only been out six
months, so I haven't heard

00:35:49.981 --> 00:35:51.510 align:middle line:90%
somebody say that on this book.

00:35:51.510 --> 00:35:54.640 align:middle line:84%
But I heard them say
that just yesterday

00:35:54.640 --> 00:35:56.480 align:middle line:84%
here at this Hay
House conference where

00:35:56.480 --> 00:35:59.840 align:middle line:84%
I was speaking, that
there was transformation,

00:35:59.840 --> 00:36:04.160 align:middle line:84%
that there was a rethinking,
that I saved them.

00:36:04.160 --> 00:36:07.640 align:middle line:84%
I hear that-- many authors
hear that many, many times.

00:36:07.640 --> 00:36:10.210 align:middle line:84%
And I remind them that it
wasn't me, that it was them.

00:36:10.210 --> 00:36:12.540 align:middle line:84%
And that it wasn't an accident
that they found my book,

00:36:12.540 --> 00:36:14.070 align:middle line:84%
or Wayne's book,
or your program.

00:36:14.070 --> 00:36:15.430 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: When the student
ready, the teacher appears.

00:36:15.430 --> 00:36:15.770 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:36:15.770 --> 00:36:16.520 align:middle line:90%
>>DOOLEY: Exactly.

00:36:16.520 --> 00:36:18.950 align:middle line:84%
We're all kind of healers,
every single person.

00:36:18.950 --> 00:36:20.440 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:36:20.440 --> 00:36:22.960 align:middle line:84%
Speaking of healers, you
write beautifully about pets.

00:36:22.960 --> 00:36:26.030 align:middle line:84%
And why is it that
when the pet goes,

00:36:26.030 --> 00:36:30.260 align:middle line:84%
it reignites the
greatest, deepest loss.

00:36:30.260 --> 00:36:31.080 align:middle line:90%
what is that?

00:36:31.080 --> 00:36:33.050 align:middle line:84%
>>DOOLEY: It's the love
that's in all of us.

00:36:33.050 --> 00:36:34.680 align:middle line:90%
We are love beings.

00:36:34.680 --> 00:36:38.310 align:middle line:84%
It's all about love,
as chapter 10 says.

00:36:38.310 --> 00:36:40.540 align:middle line:84%
And truth is the
path through love.

00:36:40.540 --> 00:36:45.290 align:middle line:84%
And it's where we have
misunderstandings that we slip,

00:36:45.290 --> 00:36:51.030 align:middle line:84%
we fall, and we suffer to
profound degrees, agonies,

00:36:51.030 --> 00:36:52.940 align:middle line:90%
through misunderstanding.

00:36:52.940 --> 00:36:56.770 align:middle line:84%
And this applies to the love
we feel for our animals.

00:36:56.770 --> 00:37:02.800 align:middle line:84%
And as much as I can share, and
anyone can realize these truth

00:37:02.800 --> 00:37:04.760 align:middle line:84%
through themselves,
we are still,

00:37:04.760 --> 00:37:07.220 align:middle line:84%
I am still, hardwired
to the illusions.

00:37:07.220 --> 00:37:11.320 align:middle line:84%
And I had to put several
beloved dogs to sleep.

00:37:11.320 --> 00:37:13.560 align:middle line:84%
And the first one
was the worst one.

00:37:13.560 --> 00:37:17.670 align:middle line:84%
I was devastated,
about six years ago.

00:37:17.670 --> 00:37:20.060 align:middle line:84%
And I was shocked
at my reaction,

00:37:20.060 --> 00:37:24.900 align:middle line:84%
knowing what I feel like I know
about reality, to have been so

00:37:24.900 --> 00:37:27.810 align:middle line:90%
affected by the loss of my dog.

00:37:27.810 --> 00:37:34.970 align:middle line:84%
But any pain we feel regarding
anything, anything in life,

00:37:34.970 --> 00:37:37.030 align:middle line:84%
is like a big red flag
that we're missing

00:37:37.030 --> 00:37:38.850 align:middle line:90%
in understanding something.

00:37:38.850 --> 00:37:42.530 align:middle line:84%
And the pain, and in
this case the loss,

00:37:42.530 --> 00:37:45.830 align:middle line:84%
whether it is a pet, or
a person, or a habit,

00:37:45.830 --> 00:37:49.930 align:middle line:84%
or whatever, is a big red
flag that, hey, you're

00:37:49.930 --> 00:37:52.210 align:middle line:84%
really doing great, but
there's this little thing here

00:37:52.210 --> 00:37:53.650 align:middle line:90%
you're misunderstanding.

00:37:53.650 --> 00:37:55.130 align:middle line:90%
Because the pet's alive.

00:37:55.130 --> 00:37:56.750 align:middle line:90%
The pet's well.

00:37:56.750 --> 00:37:59.930 align:middle line:84%
Alive within the palm
of God, so to speak.

00:37:59.930 --> 00:38:01.290 align:middle line:90%
You'll meet again.

00:38:01.290 --> 00:38:02.420 align:middle line:90%
Everything's eternal.

00:38:02.420 --> 00:38:04.020 align:middle line:90%
Everything is ongoing.

00:38:04.020 --> 00:38:05.580 align:middle line:84%
And because you're
not seeing that,

00:38:05.580 --> 00:38:08.130 align:middle line:84%
because you're so
hardwired to the illusions,

00:38:08.130 --> 00:38:10.320 align:middle line:84%
in spite of your
theoretical wisdom,

00:38:10.320 --> 00:38:12.830 align:middle line:84%
until you get further
on board with the truth,

00:38:12.830 --> 00:38:14.330 align:middle line:84%
it's going to hurt
like the Dickens.

00:38:14.330 --> 00:38:16.110 align:middle line:90%
And that's the greatest gift.

00:38:16.110 --> 00:38:18.640 align:middle line:84%
Because it's through pain,
it's through suffering,

00:38:18.640 --> 00:38:21.150 align:middle line:84%
that we can realize,
hey, I can take my life

00:38:21.150 --> 00:38:23.750 align:middle line:84%
